description:
Module based Wallpaper.

Report Bugs/Enhancements/Requests here:

https://bitbucket.org/Arthesian/wallpaper-module-visualizer/issues

en-us.ui_background_effect_hueshiftpermreset: Reset perm shift when no sound
en-us.ui_background_idlepause: Pause video when visualizer is idle
en-us.ui_background_videospeed:
Playback speed (%)
below 50% and above 400% sound doesn't work
en-us.ui_visual_bar2_rotatecolorl2r: Rotate the colors in reverse direction
en-us.ui_visual_bar_rotatecolorl2r: Rotate the colors in reverse direction
en-us.ui_visualizer_effect_hueshiftpermreset: Reset perm shift when no sound
en-us.ui_visualizer_fpscounter:
Enable FPS counter
Only works if visualizer is active
en-us.ui_visualizer_idleignoreeffects: Idle state ignores effect (eq. blur, bounce...)

zh-chs.ui_Logo: © Arthesian
zh-chs.ui_background_effect_huerotateenabled: 在拍子上启用（温度）色彩偏移
zh-chs.ui_background_effect_hueshift: 启用（烫发）低音色彩转换
zh-chs.ui_background_idlepause: 可视化器空闲时暂停视频
zh-chs.ui_background_scaletofit: 缩放以适应（而不是覆盖）
zh-chs.ui_background_videospeed:
播放速度（％）
低于50％且高于400％声音不起作用
zh-chs.ui_perpective_static: 设置静态透视图（忽略光标）
zh-chs.ui_visualizer_effect_hueshifttemp: 色温在节拍温度上移动
zh-chs.ui_visualizer_fpscounter:
启用FPS计数器
仅在可视化器处于活动状态时才可用
zh-chs.ui_visualizer_idleignoreeffects: 空闲状态忽略效果（例如模糊，反弹...）
